# About wc
# wc (short for word count) is a command in Unix-like operating systems.
#
# References:
# https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wc_(Unix)


# Count all words in a file /home/foo/bar.sh
wc /home/foo/bar.sh

# Print the byte count
wc -c /home/foo/bar.sh

# Print the line count
wc -l /home/foo/bar.sh

# Print the character count
wc -m /home/foo/bar.sh

# Print the length og longest line
wc -L /home/foo/bar.sh

# Print the word count
wc -w /home/foo/bar.sh
